# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# ku_TR.dic — Kurmanci Dictionary Word List
# Kurdish Tech Organization | Open Source
#
# FORMAT: word[/flags]
#   Flags refer to SFX/PFX rules defined in ku_TR.aff
#   A = ezafe suffix | B = plural -an | H = nisbet -î
#   D = oblique | G = agentive | P = di- prefix
#
# LANGUAGE: Kurdish Kurmanci — 100% Latin alphabet
# NOTE: This is a STARTER vocabulary (~400+ core words).
#       Expand using the Ferheng.org dataset or CLTKurmanji corpus.
#
# SOURCES FOR EXPANSION:
#   https://ferheng.org
#   https://github.com/KurdishNLP/Kurmanji-Lexicon
#   https://data.hrdag.org/KRG/
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ── Pronouns (Cînavk) ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── Common Nouns (Navdêr) ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# --- Expanded Daily, Professional & Abstract Nouns ---

# ── Nature & Geography (Xweza û Erdnîgarî) ───────────────────────────────────

# ── Family (Malbat) ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── Body Parts (Endamên Laş) ──────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── Colours (Reng) ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── Numbers (Hejmar) ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── Days & Time (Roj û Wext) ──────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── Months (Meh) ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── Common Verbs — Infinitive & Stems ────────────────────────────────────────
# Full verb morphology is handled via PFX P (di-) and SFX E
# --- Expanded Verbs ---

# ── Adjectives (Rengdêr) ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# --- Expanded Adjectives ---

# ── Adverbs (Hoker) ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── Prepositions & Particles ──────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── Conjunctions (Girêker) ────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── Proper Nouns — Places & Language ─────────────────────────────────────────

# ── Kurdish Culture & Identity ────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ── Technology Terms (Teknolojî) ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# --- Expanded Technology & Science ---

# ── Education & Literature (Xwendin û Wêje) ──────────────────────────────────

# ── Health (Tendurustî) ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────

