# END OF DICTIONARY
#
# HOW TO EXPAND THIS FILE:
#
# 1. FERHENG.ORG EXPORT:
#    Download the Kurmanci word list from https://ferheng.org
#    Format each line as: word[/FLAGS]
#
# 2. FREELANG / KURDISH NLP:
#    https://github.com/KurdishNLP/Kurmanji-Lexicon
#    Contains ~30,000 lemmatised Kurmanci entries.
#
# 3. CLARIN KURDISH CORPUS:
#    Available through CLARIN's VLO for Northern Kurdish (kmr).
#
# 4. MANUAL REVIEW:
#    All entries MUST be verified by a native Kurmanci speaker.
#    Do NOT include Sorani, Badini, or Persian words.
#    Script is 100% Latin — NO Arabic script entries.
#
# Line format: word       → no affixes (exact match only)
#              word/ABH   → allows suffix rules A, B, H from ku_TR.aff
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════#
